# Implementation Plan: Bible Data Integration

## Goal Description
Integrate the full Bible data files ([korean_bible.json](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98%20%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%20%EC%B1%85/src/data/korean_bible.json) and [english_bible.json](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98%20%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%20%EC%B1%85/src/data/english_bible.json)) into the application, replacing the current sample data ([bible_data.json](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98%20%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%20%EC%B1%85/src/data/bible_data.json)). This will provide the user with the complete Bible text in both Korean and English.

## Proposed Changes
### Bible Page Logic
-   **File**: [src/pages/BiblePage.jsx](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98%20%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%20%EC%B1%85/src/pages/BiblePage.jsx)
-   **Changes**:
    -   Import [korean_bible.json](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98%20%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%20%EC%B1%85/src/data/korean_bible.json) as `koreanBibleData`.
    -   Import [english_bible.json](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98%20%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%20%EC%B1%85/src/data/english_bible.json) as `englishBibleData`.
    -   Replace usage of `bibleData` (from [bible_data.json](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98%20%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%20%EC%B1%85/src/data/bible_data.json)) with the appropriate full dataset based on the selected language or context.
    -   Ensure the component handles the larger dataset correctly (e.g., initial load).

## Verification Plan
### Manual Verification
-   Run `npm run dev` and navigate to the Bible page.
-   Verify that the full list of Bible books is available.
-   Check that chapters and verses load correctly for both Korean and English versions.
-   Ensure smooth navigation between books and chapters.
